ZH: 我今天去公园运动。
EN: I am going to the park for exercise today.

ZH: 他每天早晨都去操场运动。
EN: He exercises at the playground every morning.

ZH: 她喜欢去游泳池运动。
EN: She enjoys exercising at the swimming pool.

ZH: 我们一起去山上运动。
EN: Let's go exercise on the mountain together.

ZH: 学生们每周都有体育课来进行各种运动项目。
EN: Students have physical education classes every week to participate in various sports.

ZH: 他非常喜欢夜跑，每晚都会去跑步。
EN: He loves running at night and goes jogging every night.

ZH: 她一直在练习体操，希望成为一名优秀的运动员。
EN: She has been practicing gymnastics, hoping to become an excellent athlete.

ZH: 我们一起去健身房做有氧运动。
EN: Let's go to the gym together for some aerobic exercise.

ZH: 他每周三会去打篮球做团体运动。
EN: He plays basketball every Wednesday for team sports.

ZH: 她在家里做瑜伽练习体姿。
EN: She practices yoga at home to improve her posture.

ZH: 我们应该积极参加各种运动项目，保持身体健康。
EN: We should actively participate in various sports to maintain good health.

ZH: 在郊外跑步是一种很好的户外运动。
EN: Running in the countryside is a great outdoor exercise.

ZH: 他在田径比赛中获得了金牌，是一名杰出的运动员。
EN: He won a gold medal in the track and field competition and is an outstanding athlete.

ZH: 她每天早上都会去晨练打羽毛球。
EN: She plays badminton in the morning as her daily exercise routine.

ZH: 大家一起来参加户外徒步运动，感受大自然的美好。
EN: Let's participate in outdoor hiking together and appreciate the beauty of nature.

ZH: 运动不仅能锻炼身体，还可以提高身心的健康。
EN: Exercise can not only strengthen the body but also improve mental health.

ZH: 我们可以在园区中做户外运动，呼吸新鲜空气。
EN: We can do outdoor exercises in the park and breathe fresh air.

ZH: 常做运动可以增强体质，减少疾病。
EN: Regular exercise can help enhance physical fitness and reduce the risk of diseases.

ZH: 我们应该鼓励年轻人积极参与各类体育运动，培养良好的运动习惯。
EN: We should encourage young people to actively participate in various sports and cultivate good exercise habits.
